63
0:03:32.208,000 --> 0:03:33,000
It's like water.

64
0:03:34.167,000 --> 0:03:35,000
It gets in places you don't want it.

65
0:03:35.917,000 --> 0:03:36,000
Human leaks.

66
0:03:37.208,000 --> 0:03:39,000
Your friends give away information about you.

67
0:03:39.375,000 --> 0:03:41,000
Your family gives away information about you.

68
0:03:42.292,000 --> 0:03:43,000
You go to a party,

69
0:03:43.583,000 --> 0:03:46,000
somebody tags you as having been there.

70
0:03:46.708,000 --> 0:03:47,000
And this is one of the ways

71
0:03:48.333,000 --> 0:03:5,000
in which abusers pick up information about you

72
0:03:50.5,000 --> 0:03:52,000
that you don't otherwise want them to know.

73
0:03:52.542,000 --> 0:03:57,000
It is not uncommon for abusers to go to friends and family

74
0:03:57.958,000 --> 0:04:,000
and ask for information about their victims

75
0:04:01.125,000 --> 0:04:04,000
under the guise of being concerned about their "mental health."

76
0:04:05.25,000 --> 0:04:08,000
A form of leak that I saw

77
0:04:08.5,000 --> 0:04:11,000
