78
0:04:11.958,000 --> 0:04:13,000
So your Gmail account,

79
0:04:14.917,000 --> 0:04:16,000
your Twitter account,

80
0:04:17.583,000 --> 0:04:19,000
your Instagram account,

81
0:04:19.833,000 --> 0:04:21,000
your iCloud,

82
0:04:22,000 --> 0:04:23,000
your Apple ID,

83
0:04:23.667,000 --> 0:04:24,000
your Netflix, your TikTok --

84
0:04:25.292,000 --> 0:04:26,000
